title: Tin Foil Hat #82: The Royal Rumble 2 with Eddie Bravo, Pat Miletich and Jeffery Wilson
description:
Thank you for tuning into another crazy Royal Rumble episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli! This episode Ryan and Sam swapcast with Pat Miletich and Jeffery Wilson of The Conspiracy Farm podcast with special guest Eddie Bravo. On this podcast we discuss....
1) Trump
2) Agents of Misinformation
3) Qanon
and of course
4) Flat Earth
Get your tickets for Live Nation Presents Tin Foil Hat Comedy Night With Sam Tripoli and Eddie Bravo live in San Fransisco at Cobbs Comedy Club. Tickets are available at CobbsComedyClub.com!
Thank you for your support.
